---
import DealerHubLayout from '../../layouts/DealerHubLayout.astro';
---
<DealerHubLayout title="Marketing Kit | Pinnacle Sales Dealer Hub" activeSection="Marketing Kit">

<h1>Marketing Kit</h1>
<p class="page-subtitle">Brand assets, social content, and resources to help you market your cabinetry brands effectively.</p>

<h2>Brand Logos & Assets</h2>
<p>Use these official brand logos on your website, social media, print materials, and showroom signage. All logos should be used as provided without modification.</p>

<div class="logo-grid">
  <div class="logo-card">
    <div class="logo-preview"><img src="/images/logos/shiloh-logo.png" alt="Shiloh Cabinetry logo" /></div>
    <h3>Shiloh Cabinetry</h3>
    <p>Face-frame cabinetry with custom finish options and traditional craftsmanship.</p>
    <div class="logo-downloads">
      <a href="/images/logos/shiloh-logo.png" download class="download-btn">PNG (Web)</a>
      <a href="/downloads/Shiloh Cabinetry TM Color.pdf" target="_blank" class="download-btn">PDF (Vector)</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="logo-card">
    <div class="logo-preview"><img src="/images/logos/eclipse-logo.png" alt="Eclipse Cabinetry logo" /></div>
    <h3>Eclipse Cabinetry</h3>
    <p>Frameless full-access cabinetry with modern European construction.</p>
    <div class="logo-downloads">
      <a href="/images/logos/eclipse-logo.png" download class="download-btn">PNG (Web)</a>
      <a href="/downloads/Eclipse Cabinetry TM Color.pdf" target="_blank" class="download-btn">PDF (Vector)</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="logo-card">
    <div class="logo-preview"><img src="/images/logos/aspect-logo.png" alt="Aspect Cabinetry logo" /></div>
    <h3>Aspect Cabinetry</h3>
    <p>Value-tier cabinetry with competitive pricing and reliable quality.</p>
    <div class="logo-downloads">
      <a href="/images/logos/aspect-logo.png" download class="download-btn">PNG (Web)</a>
      <a href="/downloads/Aspect Cabinetry TM Color.pdf" target="_blank" class="download-btn">PDF (Vector)</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="logo-card">
    <div class="logo-preview" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-muted);">Pronorm</div>
    <h3>Pronorm German Kitchens</h3>
    <p>All Pronorm marketing assets and brand guidelines available at <a href="https://pronormusa.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PronormUSA.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2>Lifestyle Photography</h2>
<p>High-resolution kitchen and bath photography available for your website, social media, and print materials. Images feature real installations with Shiloh and Eclipse cabinetry.</p>

<p>To request specific images or custom photography for your showroom installations, email <a href="mailto:marketing@pinnaclesales.biz">marketing@pinnaclesales.biz</a>.</p>

<h2>Social Media Content</h2>
<p>Ready-to-post content for your dealership's social channels. Follow and share from our brand pages:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Pinnacle Sales LinkedIn:</strong> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/pinnacle-sales-kbi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">linkedin.com/company/pinnacle-sales-kbi</a> — Industry insights, product launches, and dealer success stories</li>
  <li><strong>Shiloh Cabinetry:</strong> Follow for product launches, finish spotlights, and installation showcases</li>
  <li><strong>Eclipse Cabinetry:</strong> Modern frameless design inspiration and new product features</li>
</ul>

<p>Pinnacle Sales can also create custom social content featuring your showroom or installed projects. Reach out to discuss co-branded content opportunities.</p>

<h2>Website Content</h2>
<p>Recommended content for your dealership website to maximize SEO and client conversion:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Brand pages</strong> — Dedicated pages for each brand you carry with descriptions, key features, and sample photography</li>
  <li><strong>Project galleries</strong> — Showcase your best installations with before/after photos and project details</li>
  <li><strong>Blog content</strong> — Pinnacle Sales can provide SEO-optimized articles for your blog. See our <a href="/playbook">Kitchen Dealer Playbook</a> for content you can reference and share</li>
</ul>

<h2>Print Materials</h2>
<p>Available from WW Wood and Pinnacle Sales:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Shiloh Cabinetry product brochure</li>
  <li>Eclipse Cabinetry product brochure</li>
  <li>Finish chip display cards</li>
  <li>Door style sample boards</li>
</ul>

<p>To order print materials, contact your Pinnacle Sales territory rep.</p>

</DealerHubLayout>

<style>
  .logo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
  }
  .logo-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .logo-card h3 {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0.35rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .logo-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .logo-preview {
    background: #f9fafb;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1rem;
    min-height: 80px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .logo-preview img {
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 100px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .logo-downloads {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .download-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .download-btn::before {
    content: "⬇";
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }
  .download-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-dark);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }
</style>
